snippet.title: GRAND FINALS | NRG vs G2 | Red Bull Home Ground
snippet.description:
The biggest off-season invitational VALORANT tournament Red Bull Home Ground returns in New York with intense matchups between some of the best VALORANT teams in the world. 

Invited Teams
- FNATIC, G2, NRG, Sentinels, T1, ZETA
